nextStates

public StateSet nextStates(LabeledEvent event,
                           boolean considerEpsilonClosure)
Returns the set of states that can be reached from the current state set by transitions associated with "event".

Parameters:
considerEpsilonClosure - If true, the epsilon closure before and after "event" is also condidered, if false, only one step along transitions with event "event" is considered.
